This directory (test_legos) contains components for automatically generating
the example tests


The following files are in this directory:

MI_OPBC_neighborlist.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating neighbor lists for use with the
     MI-OPBC method.

Makefile
     This is the make file that creates the example Tests directories in the
     $KIM_TESTS_DIR directory

NEIGH_PURE_cluster_neighborlist.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating neighbor lists for use with the
     NEIGH-PURE method for free cluster systems.

NEIGH_PURE_periodic_neighborlist.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating neighbor lists for use with the
     NEIGH-PURE method for periodic FCC systems.

NEIGH_RVEC_F_cluster_neighborlist.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating neighbor lists for use with the
     NEIGH-RVEC method for free cluster systems.

NEIGH_RVEC_F_periodic_B2_neighborlist.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating neighbor lists for use with the
     NEIGH-RVEC method for periodic B2 systems.

NEIGH_RVEC_F_periodic_FCC_neighborlist.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating neighbor lists for use with the
     NEIGH-RVEC method for periodic FCC systems.

README
     This file

create_FCC_configuration.frag
     This file contains the routine for creating a cluster of atoms in a perfect
     FCC crystal configuration.

descriptor_file_input
     This file contains the input section of the KIM descriptor file.

descriptor_file_neighborlist
     This file contains the neighbor list entries of the KIM descriptor file.

descriptor_file_output
     This file contains the output section of the KIM descriptor file.

descriptor_file_start
     This file contains the beginning of the KIM descriptor file.

example_test_Ar_multiple_models/
     Directory containing the test_Ar_multiple_models Test

example_test_demo_F03/
     Directory containing the test_demo_F03 Test

get_neigh_Rij.frag
     This file contains the routine for accessing neighbor lists that include
     Rij relative position vectors.

get_neigh_no_Rij.frag
     This file contains the routine for accessing neighbor lists that do not 
     include Rij relative position vectors.

program_free_cluster.frag
     This file contains the main program for the test_*_free_cluster example
     test.

program_free_cluster_CLUSTER.frag
     This file contains the main program for the test_*_free_cluster_CLUSTER
     example test.

program_periodic_B2_NEIGH_RVEC.frag
     This file contains the main program for the test_*_periodic_B2_NEIGH_RVEC
     example test.

program_periodic_FCC_MI_OPBC.frag
     This file contains the main program for the test_*_periodic_FCC_MI_OPBC
     example test.

program_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_PURE.frag
     This file contains the main program for the test_*_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_PURE
     example test.

program_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_RVEC.frag
     This file contains the main program for the test_*_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_RVEC
     example test.

program_periodic_cut_FCC_NEIGH_RVEC.frag
     This file contains the main program for the 
     test_*_periodic_cut_FCC_NEIGH_PURE example test.

report_error.frag
     This file contain the routine that reports errors.

test_EXAMPLES.README
     This file contains a table that describes the capabilities of the example
     tests.

test_Makefile
     This file contains the Makefile that is used to generate Makefile files for
     the example tests.

test_free_cluster_README
     This file contains the README file that is used to generate REAMDE files
     for the example cluster tests.

test_periodic_B2_README
     This file contains the README file that is used to generate REAMDE files
     for the example B2 tests.

test_periodic_FCC_README
     This file contains the README file that is used to generate REAMDE files
     for the example periodic FCC tests.
